values: ok im sitting here in second period bored. I just finished the lesson i was supposed to do so i figured i would drop a line to say hi and that im bored...well i write when i get home...LATERZ

Thompson was sick, (thank god) thats mean but he is so annoying. He thinks he is funny. He is sometimes but, not all the time. Mrs. Givens is just not fun at all. I don't like school. I don't like alot of anything anymore. OH YEA MY BAND "STARSTRUCK" WILL BE MAKING OUR DEMO SOON. SO BE LOOKING OUT FOR US. Well laterz my bored friends.

Hey yall, its me again. Of course who else would it be. Today was fun. Melinda and Kay came down and I havent seen then in 4ever. I got to see Calvin and his g/f Michelle, which I said looked like a Barbie Doll. Which she did. She is so cute. LOL. She is a lil short though. Oh yea school starts back in 3 days. I can't wait. It gets so boring sittin at the house doing nothing. I would rather be with my friends. We are going to the movies Saturday. Melinda, Me, Kayla, Candice, Kelli, Micheal, and others. We are going to see FAT ALBERT. Maybe I'll run into some of my friends. I sure hope so I need to see a familiar face or I am going to die. I miss Julie. My BFF for life. She is crazy but you gotta love her. I had a good week i suppose. If you count sleeping til 1 and waking up and doing nothing good. LMAO. Well hey i gots to go...laterz.

Shanda Mason

Hey yall, im sorta depressed right now and I dont know why! I always seems to get sad when I listen to music. I just wish I could leave this frickin town and become someone new. I will be doing that in about 4 years. Im moving to Knoxville to UT. I want to become a vet. If I don't do that I still leaving this HOLE of a town. Everyone knows what you do and why you do it. In some ways that is good and in others it is bad. Becky and I are still working on getting together to make out demo. That's another way I could get out of this town. Become a singer and move far far FAR away. Maybe to Knoxville or Nashville. Somewhere where I can just start a new life away from these ppl. I love my friends but some are not my friends. Friends dont talk about each others behind their backs. Thats not a definition of a friend now is is? Julie, Whitney, Karissa, Amber, Becky, Tyler, Glen, Billy, James, Kelli, Ashley, Kat, Teri, Melanie, Anna, Whitney C., Eric, Sarah, Patrick, etc. You know who u are that I adore. But some of my "friends"(none that i metioned above)i like. I mean yea i talk to them just to be nice. But thats cause im a nice person. Well I will write again laterz. Mom is flippin so she can order some pizza...Love ya...laterz.


                       Shanda Mason
